{"tid":1047733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【理大民主牆風波】梁振英：債主追債也要用合法手段","createTime":"2019-03-05T07:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T07:31:14.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d4dd6b550b72c9c6964259ca26352a018155d0e1","tid":1047733,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190305/s00001/fa9420d0e6d1f3ebe35add48d4be6483.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190305%2Fs00001%2Ffa9420d0e6d1f3ebe35add48d4be6483.jpg&h=e8d71d6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n理工大學4名學生，去年因校內民主牆的港獨字眼被校方遮蓋，與校方人員爭論及推撞，上周五（1日）分別被罰退學、停學一年和「社會服務令」。理大校友、其後曾任理大校董會主席的前特首梁振英，今日（5日）在facebook第二次發文回應事件，指這些學生被罰，是因反對方式違反校規及法律。梁並以「債主追債」作類比解釋，指需以合法手段表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英在文中稱，理大學生並非由於反對學校的行政而被罰，而是因反對方式和手法違反校規，甚至違反法律，「債主追債也要用合法手段，如果在債仔門口淋紅油，就是刑事毁壞，可以被判入獄，如果淋紅油的是大學生，法官大概會加重刑罰」。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英上周六（2日）在facebook發文首次評論事件。就有報章引述被退學的學生何俊謙說：「我哋只係想香港好似以前咁美好，有言論自由」，梁在該帖文回應，指是「年輕人被洗腦後的荒謬，我們不能坐視」。<br />\n<br />\n(梁振英fb)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190305/s00001/1551762655031/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190305%2Fs00001%2F1551762655031%2F&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcakzYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=6f436f33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190305%2Fs00001%2F1551762655031%2F&h=6d76de98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190305/s00001/1551762655031/</a>"},{"pid":"369beff8c7f6a4cc2755602b0902ca32b8ab0bb6","tid":1047733,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:12:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講俾UGL聽？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"de2718f41d3bd23c348d45f7d29dff8836321189","tid":1047733,"uid":130695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"呢件廢老中坑走火入魔 奶共癡撚線<br />\n幾時推哂全家出黎俾中共享用"},{"pid":"002e5ab68844f7c4e88e65b341bea1c9ea7a7db4","tid":1047733,"uid":19725,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:13:49.000Z","msg":"老老77 其實佢講得無錯<br />\n人民抗命就係冒住犯法／犯例既風險去爭取自己想要既野<br />\n爭取到咪英雄，爭取唔到咪作反<br />\n2千年黎都係咁run <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只怪關ching 唔夠激進<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb1b03b2e36ec47248854b009237ab96a14a75b","tid":1047733,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"002e5ab68844f7c4e88e65b341bea1c9ea7a7db4","tid":1047733,"uid":19725,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:13:49.000Z","msg":"老老77 其實佢講得無錯<br />\n人民抗命就係冒住犯法／犯例既風險去爭取自己想要既野<br />\n爭取到咪英雄，爭取唔到咪作反<br />\n2千年黎都係咁run <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只怪關ching 唔夠激進<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:14:18.000Z","msg":"預左多負評，利申反共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8055dedca594e5e28f8c0efc32cbadfd2926047","tid":1047733,"uid":12